  "monologue": "High-level rationale: The user is practicing structured urge-tolerance within BED-focused routines. Providing a brief start cue and reinforcing mid-session checks supports self-regulation without adding cognitive burden, aligning with the goal of nudging the behavior score toward the target while preserving compassion and routine.",
